# TIPTAP VPS MCP mapping

This workspace folder is **TAPTAP TZ** (Tanzania). Use only the VPS MCP servers listed for this project.

## This project uses

| MCP server name (exact) | Host | Use for |
|-------------------------|------|---------|
| **TIPTAP TZ** | `164.92.242.245` — `tiptapafrica.co.tz` | Laravel TZ web: Docker, nginx, MySQL, `.env`, `php artisan`, deploy from [Tiptaptz](https://github.com/ESNyarobi123/Tiptaptz) |
| **TITAPtz bot** | `178.62.61.85` — `wa-notify.tiptapafrica.co.tz` | WhatsApp bot TZ (`tiptopbot`), bot Docker, Node logs, `/notify` |

When the user asks to deploy **Laravel / site / dashboard** for Tanzania, use **`TIPTAP TZ`** only.
When the user asks to deploy or restart the **WhatsApp bot** for TZ, use **`TITAPtz bot`** only.

## Do not use for TAPTAP TZ (unless user explicitly names another project)

| MCP server | Belongs to |
|------------|------------|
| **TIPTAP SOUTH AFRICA** | `TAPTAP_sauth` (South Africa Laravel app) |
| **TIPTAP Saloon** | `Saloon ver` (Saloon Laravel app) |

Never deploy TZ code to South Africa or Saloon VPS, and never use those MCP servers for TZ bot work by default.

## How to invoke

Use `CallMcpTool` with `server` set to the exact MCP name (e.g. `"TITAPtz bot"`). Read the tool schema under the MCP descriptors before calling.

## Related local paths (TZ)

- Laravel app: this repo root
- WhatsApp bot: `tiptopbot/` or repo `TipTap_tz_bot` — runs on **TITAPtz bot**
